    <listitem>
      <para>Issues were encountered in trying to retrieve latest version of the tile.</para>
    </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
</variablelist>
<para>
<figure>
<title>Cache Status Overlay: Example</title>
<screenshot>
  <graphic format="PNG" fileref="figures/Maps_Cache_Status_Overlay.png"/>
</screenshot>
</figure>
</para>
<para>
  If desired, the colours used for the disk map cache overlay indicators can be altered via the advanced configuration in <xref linkend="misc_settings"/>.
</para>
</section>

